@baseUrl = https://localhost:7180

### Get all hotels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Hotels
Accept: application/json

### Create hotel
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Hotels
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Zagreb Central Rooms",
  "price": 55,
  "latitude": 45.8131,
  "longitude": 15.9775
}

### Search hotels near Zagreb under 100 euros
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Hotels/search?prompt=I need a hotel near Zagreb under 100 euros&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json